{"4293020": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "表妹的心動嬉戲", "steam_appid": 4293020, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b413fa98198e79ae1929bb9203ee066c.poster.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b413fa98198e79ae1929bb9203ee066c.webm?t=1769776468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b413fa98198e79ae1929bb9203ee066c.mp4?t=1769776468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/de7dab7e69278b9bc83ab15b68a302a0.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個炎熱的夏天，阿姨來家裡做客，還帶著你可愛的小表妹一起。看到父母在一旁聊天，你擔心她會覺得無聊，於是主動邀請她過來和你一起玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/c17f1aa9cd2172f7dff7fc2c077e70da.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >歡迎來到這款可愛的摸頭模擬遊戲。你可以和表妹一起聊天，輕輕地摸摸她的頭，但記得要小心，千萬別碰她的布偶，不然她會不高興。你們能相處的時間不多，所以要在她離開前，盡量讓她保持開心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b3afa6876abd4a20009ded14dd39f08b.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/454e7b15b8d283e0d2cd4931c5bfe3a5.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可愛的動畫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你摸她頭的時候，可以看到穗佳生動可愛的表情和動作反應。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用與穗佳互動獲得的點數來解鎖新的技能，並延長你們能夠相處的時間。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自動模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲支援自動模式。 </p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b413fa98198e79ae1929bb9203ee066c.poster.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b413fa98198e79ae1929bb9203ee066c.webm?t=1769776468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b413fa98198e79ae1929bb9203ee066c.mp4?t=1769776468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/de7dab7e69278b9bc83ab15b68a302a0.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個炎熱的夏天，阿姨來家裡做客，還帶著你可愛的小表妹一起。看到父母在一旁聊天，你擔心她會覺得無聊，於是主動邀請她過來和你一起玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/c17f1aa9cd2172f7dff7fc2c077e70da.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >歡迎來到這款可愛的摸頭模擬遊戲。你可以和表妹一起聊天，輕輕地摸摸她的頭，但記得要小心，千萬別碰她的布偶，不然她會不高興。你們能相處的時間不多，所以要在她離開前，盡量讓她保持開心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/b3afa6876abd4a20009ded14dd39f08b.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/extras/454e7b15b8d283e0d2cd4931c5bfe3a5.avif?t=1769776468\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可愛的動畫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你摸她頭的時候，可以看到穗佳生動可愛的表情和動作反應。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用與穗佳互動獲得的點數來解鎖新的技能，並延長你們能夠相處的時間。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自動模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲支援自動模式。 </p>", "short_description": "在這款療癒系的模擬遊戲裡，你將趁父母在旁邊聊天的時候跟表妹一起穗佳打發時間。可以摸摸她的頭、陪她聊聊天、聊聊彼此喜歡的東西，不過千萬別碰她的玩偶哦！你得在有限時間內把穗香哄開心才行。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/f7b813f2839e5c90db1c0d0b76e907607874621a/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1769776468", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/7b88738c846b57a63d7387994dedbea2d0db2510/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1769776468", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4293020/7b88738c846b57a63d7387994dedbea2d